ygData.messageBody:
Well Kathy ma'friend WELCOME!

We can use all the help and friends we can get! Come over to E'ci and
I'll buy you a town..um..beer...haha! Im Sandy (me a man) ! I play a Wood
Elf warrior (Female) named Jadeeyes, who has had the misfortune of grouping
with all the wrong people! My 15th levels slips between 14th and 15th so
often I feel like a YO YO! ARGH!
It seems too quiet today for SOME REASON and Im glad you spoke up and
said HELLO!

Take care now!

Sandy Collier (Mister to the underpowered!)
